---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import EmergencyBanner from '../../../components/EmergencyBanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Palpitations — Dr Delhasse, Cardiologist" description="Heart palpitations: when to see a cardiologist? Discover the causes and management of cardiac rhythm disorders." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home', href:'/en'}, {label:'Symptoms', href:'/en/symptoms'}, {label:'Palpitations'}]} />
      <h1><span class="text-primary">Palpitations</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">When your heart races</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <EmergencyBanner lang="en" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/detail/palpitations.webp" alt="Palpitations consultation" class="detail-hero-img" />
      <img src="/images/svg/symptomes/Palpitaciones.svg" alt="Palpitations" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>A heart that beats too hard is not always a sign of emotion. Stress, fatigue, caffeine or alcohol can be the cause. But sometimes a cardiac rhythm disorder or an underlying condition is at play. If these sensations are frequent, bothersome or associated with pain, fainting or breathlessness, a cardiology assessment is essential. Early diagnosis helps identify the source of the problem and establish appropriate management to control heart rhythm and ensure optimal quality of life.</p>

      <p>When in doubt or if symptoms are concerning, it is better not to wait and to consult immediately.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/symptoms" class="btn btn--outline-dark">&larr; All symptoms</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-hero-img { width: 100%; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
